1. *Prirodi* se brzo oporavljaju nakon požara. (Nature* quickly recovers after fires.)
2. *Prirodi* nije mesto u kavezima. (Nature* doesn't belong in cages.)
3. Svaki deo *prirode* je važan za održavanje ekosistema. (Every part of *nature* is important for maintaining the ecosystem.)
4. Planina Tara je jedno od najlepših mesta u *prirodi*. (Mount Tara is one of the most beautiful places in *nature*.)
5. Naša firma se bavi očuvanjem *prirode*. (Our company is engaged in nature conservation.)
6. Istraživači proučavaju različite aspekte *prirode*. (Researchers study different aspects of *nature*.)
7. Živim u malom gradu okruženom *prirodom*. (I live in a small town surrounded by *nature*.)
8. Naša škola organizuje ekskurziju u *prirodu*. (Our school is organizing a field trip to *nature*.)
9. Ljudi treba da poštuju *prirodu* i brinu o njoj. (People should respect *nature* and take care of it.)
10. Mnogi ljudi uživaju u boravku u *prirodi* tokom leta. (Many people enjoy spending time in *nature* during the summer.)